              "value": "={{ [ { \"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"Returns ONLY a valid JSON array containing exactly 1 active social impact grant. Strict Rules: 1. The grant MUST be from the current year (2026). 2. The grant MUST be currently OPEN, available, and NOT expired. Do not include past or closed calls. 3. Format: [{ 'title':'...', 'description':'...', 'sourceUrl':'...' }]\" }, { \"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Find exactly one currently open grant for NGOs in Latin America for the year 2026.\\\\n\\\\nCRITICAL RULE: YOU MUST NOT RETURN ANY OF THESE KNOWN GRANTS: \" + $('Consultar Memoria (No Repetir)').all().map(i => i.json.title).slice(0, 15).join(', ') + \". Pick a completely DIFFERENT, obscure, or highly specific grant (e.g. Health, Youth, Clean Technology, Women, Climate, Agriculture, Water). Your choice MUST BE DIFFERENT from the excluded list.\" } ] }}"
